title: Finn’s Website
text:
Welcome to my website. My name is Finn and I am an emerging data scientist. I am an undergraduate student at the University of Toronto studying Information. How did I get here? Well, I used to study physics at McMaster and when I was given the opportunity to study generative adversarial networks in a medical context, I fell in love with artificial intelligence, motivating my transfer of studies to learn to leverage the power of data.
My interests include: generative artificial intelligence, sustainable energy
